c: 5
v: 107
t: "Tokkel diggah num kak Rabe mari tama Namma numuk farrimtut hinnay Sumaaqat dirab kee ganot keenik Radeeniih dambi cakkisitaanam keenik yubleenik, toysa num kak Rabe marak Namma num Sumaaqah ken Aracat Solta kay nagra cakkķisita marak, tokkel ken Nammay: usun diraabah yaceen Sumaaqak Ni Sumaq Nummah aysuk Raaqaah nanu abna Sumaaqat cakkik madardarinnino, diggah toysa nanu tamahat dirab neceek daalimiinik marak teyna kinnino Axcuk Yallal xiibitan"